### To check the health status of the API server
GET http://localhost:8082//api/health

### Register User
POST http://localhost:8082/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:8082/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

### Create Book (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

{
  "title": "The Great Gatsby",
  "author": "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
  "genre": "Classic",
  "coverimage": "https://example.com/cover.jpg",
  "file": "https://example.com/book.pdf"
}
